{"tid":871244,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[求指點] 買赤道儀","createTime":"2018-10-21T18:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T04:16:36.000Z","uid":201299,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9da7e269281cbd978a68fb442d6d2ab7cba7769d","tid":871244,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:11:01.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我由細到大玩開天文，都玩咗十二三年，但係一直都對天文攝影冇乜深入研究，可能係我對攝影冇乜特別嘅熱誠啦，之前剩係試過用相機駁望遠鏡影下月球、用遠古時代嘅QHY5影下火星土星咁，一直都冇接觸過深空天體呢part。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近突然間諗到，既然玩咗咁耐天文，點解唔試下鑽研下影深空呢？所以而家想買返隻赤道儀，最好連架啦，唔洗玩到高橋嗰啲high end嘢，抬得起我枝Sky Watcher 6吋反射鏡同埋80mm ED APO就夠，或者我之後會想upgrade下啲器材，可能會考慮CFF105又或者玩下CCD咁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBudget就大概預六千左右以內啦，仲有就係會驚個mount太重，抬出街有難度，自己又冇車牌，行動方面都係一大難題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前碌下碌下見到呢款Sky Watcher EQM-35 <a href=\"http://www.skywatcherusa.com/product/eqm-35-mount/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skywatcherusa.com%2Fproduct%2Feqm-35-mount%2F&d=6CJtOGdq%2BlGd4BqvTH7inZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6ae5190e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.skywatcherusa.com/product/eqm-35-mount/</a> ，諗唔諗得過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c13a2a800e30690834740a4ca6b296174f5348d","tid":871244,"uid":199244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba5cf169a7076465ccdcfd0825214fe6010e8e9","tid":871244,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl